Term,Notes
# Hate speech terms only. One term per row in the Term column.
# Bad language / profanity goes in bad-language-terms.csv (same format).
# Political terms go in political-terms.csv (same format).
# Pornographic or sexual terms go in sexual-terms.csv (same format).
# Opens in Excel or Google Sheets. Lines starting with # are ignored.
